Quickstrike:



Quickstrike watched as Inferno shot Megatron's head off. "Whoa! Nice 
shot!" He got out of the other's way when they took Megatron off. He 
turned his attention to Black Arachnia when he went to the entrance. 

Quickstuff? He never heard that one before. 

He had to say it.

"Megatron called me uh roach!" He was insulted when he said 
that. "Ah'm uh arachnid!" He soon bowed his head. Some Predacons 
didn't like bots with big mouths that complained. And he certainly 
didn't want to be hit by Black Arachnia. "Ah'll shut up."
